PlayDate! Website 

PlayDate is a 3-page website designed to help moms connect, plan play dates and discover new activites for their toddlers. 

Pages
-Home Page
-Activities Page
-About Us Page

Features
-Nav bar linking to all pages
-Login & Sign-up forms 
-Dropdown menu for user interests 
-Activity cards with images
-Event table showing activities
-GIF for visual engagment 
-Responsive layout using flexbox
-CSS styling with animations


Technologies Used 
-HTML
-CSS

Author
Michia-Gaye Padilla